{"tid":2026800,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍2支航母打擊群赴西太平洋執行警戒任務","createTime":"2020-05-21T07:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T08:23:06.000Z","uid":21470,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d70edfaa3afe76c73120234710871720cff3d3e3","tid":2026800,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"美軍2支航母打擊群赴西太平洋執行警戒任務<br />\n21.05.2020 14:58<br />\n<br />\n中美兩國關係因新型冠狀病毒疫情持續倒退之際，美軍先後派遣兩艘航空母艦，到西太平洋區執行警戒任務；部署在日本的列根號航母打擊群，今日駛離橫須賀基地，到西太平洋地區活動。列根號早前有至少16名官兵確診感染新型冠狀病毒，橫須賀基地在3月一度封閉。<br />\n<br />\n而有1000多名官兵確診的羅斯福號航母，在關島停泊近兩個月後，今天開赴菲律賓海執行任務，艦上官兵人數則由5000多人，減至約4000人；指揮官說，打擊群有能力在印太地區執行任務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289059&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289059%26csid%3D261_367&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=2a46a64f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289059&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"94cd51e8d098d8302a698ffca8d523777c3429b0","tid":2026800,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:42:34.000Z","msg":"勁！<br />\n<br />\n加多一個航母打擊群, 就可以開波！"},{"pid":"4dcce7f101db45622e34ca6fd3c5aae4b7518b91","tid":2026800,"uid":122377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:43:35.000Z","msg":"真係開波會咁高調咩"},{"pid":"8f7d32cf8c4b872fa58fc7116a966b1216e50dac","tid":2026800,"uid":51057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國海軍太平洋艦隊命令大量核潛艇前往西太平洋<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2026189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2026189</a>"},{"pid":"467fd72ac2d8be8faddbad1f0b2727a2ec8373c2","tid":2026800,"uid":89517